Required php extensions : 
php5-imagick
php5-gd (not sure)
php-gettext


Translation functions needs locale packages to be installed on the server : 
apt-get install language-pack-en-base
apt-get install language-pack-fr-base
apt-get install language-pack-de-base
apt-get install language-pack-it-base
apt-get install language-pack-................-base